				<div class="bible-name">The Holy Bible â DouayâRheims version</div>
				<div class="book-name">The First Epistle of St. Paul to the Thessalonians</div>
				<div class="act-chapter">
					<div class="prev-chapter"><a href="https://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/NT/1_Th/10352">&lt; prev</a></div>|
					<div class="chapter">Chapter 3</div>
